===Noun===
'''mule'''
# a generally [[sterile]] [[hybrid]] [[offspring]] of a male [[donkey]] and a female [[horse]].
#''(Slang):'' A [[stubborn]] person
# ''(Slang):'' A [[person]] paid to [[smuggle]] drugs.

